c: 16
v: 94
t: "Kandi ntimuzagire indahiro zanyu uburyo bwo kuriganya hagati yanyu, bityo ikirenge (cyanyu) kitazavaho kikanyerera (kiva muri Isilamu) nyuma y’uko cyari gishikamye (mu kwemera), maze mugasogongera ikibi (ibihano byo ku isi) kubera ko mwakumiriye (abantu) kugana inzira ya Allah, ndetse mukazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye"